.TH LOOTSHEET-LOOT-RECOGNIZE 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-loot-recognize \\- Recognize an appraisal on-ledger
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet loot recognize [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet loot recognize --appraisal-id ID --date YYYY-MM-DD [--description TEXT]

Examples:
  lootsheet loot recognize --appraisal-id appraisal-123 --date 2026-03-10
  lootsheet loot recognize --appraisal-id appraisal-123 --date 2026-03-10 --description "Recognize moonstone inventory"
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
--appraisal-id=string
appraisal ID (required) (default: )
.TP
--date=string
recognition date in YYYY-MM-DD (required) (default: )
.TP
--description=string
optional description (default: )
.TP
-h, --help
help for recognize
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet-loot(1)
